    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone looking for a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a few small dings on the passenger side doors. Inside, the cabin is well-used but clean, with visible wear on the driver\u2019s seat upholstery and some minor staining on the rear floor mats. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly, though it may soon require routine maintenance for items like brake pads and tires. It is a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
