    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into excellence with this absolutely stunning vehicle! It is in mint condition, looking and driving just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, offering you a truly pristine driving experience that is rare to find. This is a top-tier choice for anyone seeking a car in showroom-quality condition!",
