    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are no scratches, dents, or chips to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, with leather that looks and feels brand new and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, offering a driving experience that is as smooth and responsive as the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle of this caliber in truly exceptional state.",
      "price": 48500.0,
